    "description": "GreenBee, Inc. provides green and digital transformation and technology licensing services in Japan. It provides green transformation products and solutions, including EV and quick chargers, industrial and home energy storage systems, risen hyper-ion solar panels, and smart data logger devices. The company also offers digital transformation services, such as GreenBee Cloud Backup, a subscription-based cloud backup service for smartphones; and Risk Finder, which supports secure Android app development. In addition, it provides Embedded Browser Tourbillon, a browser solution for broadcasting services; VAlution BD, a Blu-ray disc playback software for embedded applications; sMedio True BD/True DVD, a Blu-ray disc player app for Windows; sMedio TV Suite for Windows, a DTCP-IP player app; sMedio Data Transfer, a file transfer with QR code; and sMedio DTCP MOVE, a video management application for NAS devices. The company was formerly known as sMedio, Inc. and changed its name to GreenBee, Inc. in April 2024. The company was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan."
